    <item>
      <title>乌克兰-俄罗斯天然气过境协议面临关键时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ukraine-russia-gas-transit-deal-faces-critical-moment-of-truth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰天然气运输的未来正处于转折点。如果周三之前不能达成最后协议，数十亿立方米的天然气运输可能会中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/ukraine-russia-gas-transit-deal-faces-critical-moment-of-truth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大部长在海湖庄园向卢特尼克介绍边境问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/canadian-ministers-take-border-pitch-to-lutnick-at-mar-a-lago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名加拿大高级内阁部长飞往佛罗里达州，向美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的团队陈述北部边境是安全的，不需要征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-28/canadian-ministers-take-border-pitch-to-lutnick-at-mar-a-lago</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Dec 2024 00:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦称财政部将在 1 月中旬达到新的债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/yellen-says-treasury-to-hit-new-debt-limit-in-mid-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，财政部很可能在 1 月中旬某个时候开始采取特殊会计措施，以避免突破美国债务上限，并敦促立法者采取行动捍卫美国的“充分信任和信用”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/yellen-says-treasury-to-hit-new-debt-limit-in-mid-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克与特朗普盟友的移民斗争席卷社交媒体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/musk-s-immigration-fight-with-trump-allies-engulfs-social-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场有关移民政策的激烈网络辩论，暴露了唐纳德·特朗普的硅谷支持者（包括亿万富翁顾问埃隆·马斯克）与其狂热反移民群体之间日益扩大的裂痕，预示着这位当选总统在其标志性政策问题上将面临的艰难、有时甚至相互矛盾的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/musk-s-immigration-fight-with-trump-allies-engulfs-social-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 21:02:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克威胁乌克兰若断气将断电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/slovakia-threatens-ukraine-with-power-cuts-over-gas-flow-halt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐威胁说，如果基辅停止向中欧输送俄罗斯天然气，斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐将切断对乌克兰的电力供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/slovakia-threatens-ukraine-with-power-cuts-over-gas-flow-halt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 18:56:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国计划针对中国电信黑客采取更多行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/us-plans-more-actions-targeting-china-for-salt-typhoon-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫官员周五表示，美国已确定第九家电信公司受到中国大规模间谍活动的影响，并计划采取进一步措施遏制来自北京的网络攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/us-plans-more-actions-targeting-china-for-salt-typhoon-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 17:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员称乌克兰可能在数月内失去其占领的所有俄罗斯土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/russia-ukraine-war-moscow-could-soon-retake-all-of-kursk-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员称，在今年早些时候的突然袭击之后，乌克兰军队已经失去了在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区占领的大约一半领土，并可能在几个月内失去其余地区，这可能会使基辅失去与俄罗斯进行停火谈判的重要筹码。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/russia-ukraine-war-moscow-could-soon-retake-all-of-kursk-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 17:02:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师押注加拿大多伦多证券交易所明年将因利率下降而达到 28,000 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/strategists-bet-canada-s-tsx-will-hit-28-000-next-year-as-rates-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大投资策略师预计，尽管唐纳德·特朗普新政府可能实施关税，给经济带来压力，但该国主要股指明年仍将保持强劲势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/strategists-bet-canada-s-tsx-will-hit-28-000-next-year-as-rates-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
